XfrpIdAndTypeOpt = object
  case kind*: XfrpIdAndTypeOptKind
  of XfrpIdAndTypeOptKind.IdWithExplicitType:
      idExplicit*: XfrpAst[XfrpId]
      tyExplicit*: XfrpAst[XfrpType]

  of XfrpIdAndTypeOptKind.IdWithoutAnyTypeAnnot:
      idImplicit*: XfrpAst[XfrpId]

XfrpLiteralKind {...}{.pure.} = enum
  LitUnit, LitBool, LitInt, LitFloat
  Source Edit 
XfrpLiteral = object
  case kind*: XfrpLiteralKind
  of XfrpLiteralKind.LitUnit:
      nil

  of XfrpLiteralKind.LitBool:
      boolVal*: bool

  of XfrpLiteralKind.LitInt:
      intVal*: int

  of XfrpLiteralKind.LitFloat:
      floatVal*: float

XfrpBinOp = enum
  binAdd = "+", binEqEq = "==", binVertVert = "||", binLte = "<=", binLt = "<",
  binGte = ">=", binGt = ">"
  Source Edit 
XfrpExprKind {...}{.pure.} = enum
  ExprLiteral, ExprId, ExprAnnot, ExprBin, ExprIf, ExprApp
  Source Edit 
XfrpExpr = object
  case kind*: XfrpExprKind
  of XfrpExprKind.ExprLiteral:
      litVal*: XfrpAst[XfrpLiteral]

  of XfrpExprKind.ExprId:
      id*: XfrpAst[XfrpId]

  of XfrpExprKind.ExprAnnot:
      annotId*: XfrpAst[XfrpId]
      annot*: XfrpAst[XfrpAnnotation]

  of XfrpExprKind.ExprBin:
      binOp*: XfrpAst[XfrpBinOp]
      binLhs*: ref XfrpAst[XfrpExpr]
      binRhs*: ref XfrpAst[XfrpExpr]

  of XfrpExprKind.ExprIf:
      ifExpr*: ref XfrpAst[XfrpExpr]
      thenExpr*: ref XfrpAst[XfrpExpr]
      elseExpr*: ref XfrpAst[XfrpExpr]

  of XfrpExprKind.ExprApp:
      appId*: XfrpAst[XfrpId]
      appArgs*: seq[XfrpAst[XfrpExpr]]
  Source Edit

  DefNode, DefFunc

XfrpDefinition = object
  case kind*: XfrpDefinitionKind
  of XfrpDefinitionKind.DefNode:
      nodeIdAndTypeOpt*: XfrpAst[XfrpIdAndTypeOpt]
      nodeInit*: Option[XfrpAst[XfrpExpr]]
      nodeBody*: XfrpAst[XfrpExpr]

  of XfrpDefinitionKind.DefFunc:
      funId*: XfrpAst[XfrpId]
      funRetType*: XfrpAst[XfrpType]
      funArgs*: seq[XfrpAst[XfrpIdAndType]]
      funBody*: XfrpAst[XfrpExpr]
  Source Edit

XfrpInput = object
  case kind*: XfrpInputKind
  of XfrpInputKind.InputWithoutInit:
      idAndTypeNoInit*: XfrpAst[XfrpIdAndType]

  of XfrpInputKind.InputWithInit:
      idAndTypeWithInit*: XfrpAst[XfrpIdAndType]
      init*: XfrpAst[XfrpExpr]
